  "body": "Bugfixes:\r\n* Don't detect `SessionLeader` as terminal, actually (Terminal, Linux)\r\n* Fix blurry chafa result when specifying both width and height (#757, Logo)\r\n\r\nFeatures:\r\n* Support new MacBook Air (Host, macOS)\r\n* Distinguish min frequency and base frequency (CPU)\r\n\r\nLogo:\r\n* Fix proxmox\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n<details><summary>SHA256SUMs</summary><br>\r\n\r\n```\r\n70cf3c30d0cc19a4c0f5a5ab35bde0db7d76b31e6d62435bd8c9cfc40f409079  fastfetch-freebsd-aarch64/fastfetch-freebsd-aarch64.tar.gz\r\ncbbc510fe66edbb594a838438fa8eb8baa76710bf27e191de25d8ea250f606b0  fastfetch-freebsd-aarch64/fastfetch-freebsd-aarch64.zip\r\n4cdea6ab8ad72516a4904ed9f3728d5879bdac9139ea7c8124fee0bbd39ff138  fastfetch-freebsd-amd64/fastfetch-freebsd-amd64.tar.gz\r\n152c36bdce6c9c4c063766753cd869a516d14e2caf13617f0fa8570b05496475  fastfetch-freebsd-amd64/fastfetch-freebsd-amd64.zip\r\n1b19c48f65a029781fae586e0a34917d53957625d25b2363c24b9d4d3274324a  fastfetch-linux-aarch64/fastfetch-linux-aarch64.deb\r\ncd22927ca9e1ef9c0e28442c4d580f1b27b7c8622468ec88928db1cafa25c528  fastfetch-linux-aarch64/fastfetch-linux-aarch64.rpm\r\n184ce8c3e5f4e24df47b8c3b1cc9bfe4e0793c65a2a752d565cf8061f237e523  fastfetch-linux-aarch64/fastfetch-linux-aarch64.tar.gz\r\n806c0fa931764b50fd8c402e9613cfd7cdc4d179af00ddca26b17a31e873806d  fastfetch-linux-aarch64/fastfetch-linux-aarch64.zip\r\n487482b9cbe839b000ec8559cadbb81bee1ec09a65454991b09b22f952c9946a  fastfetch-linux-amd64/fastfetch-linux-amd64.deb\r\ne7c238e67c8c422efd1a424d099423474ca7670076399ceb3d2160db13156d87  fastfetch-linux-amd64/fastfetch-linux-amd64.rpm\r\n7432a06212d42948342727eeaada8a99358a5acabb8aacd293c2494cbe865e01  fastfetch-linux-amd64/fastfetch-linux-amd64.tar.gz\r\n58dc9f78f2682383b3c3aeeb23cd058ebddceda4b9d7a891efe0d18073897314  fastfetch-linux-amd64/fastfetch-linux-amd64.zip\r\n93d0c8709e2d7e03dfc4b2a7b56137d10bcfa4e2194d7f22a1af0d1edbf97b10  fastfetch-macos-universal/fastfetch-macos-universal.tar.gz\r\nb54fff8b7c9fbccfada6